OL,3,CWilliam brings cakes as hill farmers
OL,4,Cshare challenges of diversifying
OL,6,FThe Prince of Wales took a box of
OL,7,Fcakes when he met hill farmers in the
OL,8,FYorkshire Dales and discussed the
OL,9,Fchallenges facing their industry.
OL,11,FWilliam visited Adam Hunter, 37, who
OL,12,Fkeeps sheep and cattle at Crow Trees
OL,13,FFarm in Swaledale, which he farms with
OL,14,Fhis wife Leanne and their children
OL,15,FAnnie and Ted.
OL,17,FLike many farmers in the area, the
OL,18,Ffamily has diversified the business
OL,19,Fand has converted a barn into a
OL,20,Fbunkhouse, which sleeps 27.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/7
