PN,42304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1778061972
OL,3,CWilliam brings cakes as hill farmers
OL,4,Cshare challenges of diversifying
OL,6,FThe Prince of Wales, who as Duke of
OL,7,FCornwall is a major landowner,
OL,8,Fdiscussed with the group the different
OL,9,Fpractices favoured by older and
OL,10,Fyounger farmers.
OL,12,FAddressing the Metcalfe father and
OL,13,Fson, he said: "You clearly have a good
OL,14,Frelationship, not every generation I
OL,15,Fhave seen has that."
OL,17,FAfter the visit, Mr Hunter told
OL,18,Freporters: "He understood the area and
OL,19,Funderstood a lot more than you would
OL,20,Fthink."
OL,26,@uD@OOUwD@TO]zD@LOU|D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
