OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,424,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1778061972
OL,3,CWilliam brings cakes as hill farmers
OL,4,Cshare challenges of diversifying
OL,6,FHe explained how farmers maintain the
OL,7,Fbeauty of the dale, which makes it so
OL,8,Fattractive to visitors, and if they
OL,9,Fwere not supported, there was no one
OL,10,Felse to step into the role.
OL,12,FHe said: "We are the cheapest park-
OL,13,Fkeepers that the government can have.
OL,15,F"There's no tourism here without
OL,16,Ffarmers."
OL,18,FAfter speaking to the prince, Mrs
OL,19,FWaggett, who works in a primary
OL,20,Fschool, told reporters: "It felt like
OL,21,Fhe was on our side."
OL,26,@tD@JOUwD@AOUxD@IO]|D@YOU}D@TO]
