OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1778061972
OL,3,CWilliam brings cakes as hill farmers
OL,4,Cshare challenges of diversifying
OL,6,FLater, William dropped into
OL,7,FBainbridge, a Wensleydale village, to
OL,8,Flook at a community project that
OL,9,Fgenerates electricity from a hydro-
OL,10,Fplant.
OL,12,FSince 2011, an Archimedes screw in the
OL,13,FRiver Bain has created enough power
OL,14,Ffor 30 local homes.
OL,16,FAfterwards, William visited Hammonds
OL,17,FButchers and spoke to well-wishers on
OL,18,Fthe village green.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/7
