OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F423A1778061972
OL,3,CWilliam brings cakes as hill farmers
OL,4,Cshare challenges of diversifying
OL,6,FRetired engineer Tom Fairey, who is a
OL,7,Fdirector of the hydro-plant, said
OL,8,Fafterwards: "He asked a lot of
OL,9,Fsensible and intuitive questions."
OL,11,FThis is the Talking Royals - our
OL,12,Fweekly podcast about the royal family,
OL,13,Fwith ITV News Royal Editor Chris Ship
OL,14,Fand Producer Lizzie Robinson
